985
01:23:10,001 --> 01:23:13,421
Nothing without you.
You're a senior officer, a department head.

986
01:23:13,504 --> 01:23:16,882
- TSO's with Hunter.
- You have keys to the small arms locker.

987
01:23:16,924 --> 01:23:21,512
Now, we want to recruit a few more men
and then we're gonna open that arsenal.

988
01:23:21,595 --> 01:23:24,307
I just talked to the captain in his room.

989
01:23:24,390 --> 01:23:28,728
He specifically asked for you.
He says we cannot go without you.

990
01:23:30,062 --> 01:23:32,690
I don't believe this.

991
01:23:33,941 --> 01:23:36,777
