01:25:17,461 --> 01:25:20,089
- Send a man and find Zimmer.
- Aye, sir.

1006
01:25:20,172 --> 01:25:23,509
- Get a side arm.
- Aye, aye, sir.

1007
01:25:23,592 --> 01:25:25,386
- Chief Young.
- Aye, Chief.

1008
01:25:27,847 --> 01:25:29,807
Turn around.

1009
01:25:31,058 --> 01:25:33,102
At ease, sailor.

1010
01:25:40,901 --> 01:25:42,820
- Sir.
- Thank you, Mr. Ince.

1011
01:25:43,988 --> 01:25:45,948
- Mr. Westergaurd.
- Sir.

1012
01:25:46,407 --> 01:25:48,993
- Mr. Zimmer.
- Ready, sir.

1013
01:25:50,036 --> 01:25:52,538
Let's get on with it.

1014
01:25:53,664 --> 01:25:56,751
Stand guard.

1015
01:26:01,547 --> 01:26:04,508
All you people,
return to your stations.

1016
01:26:04,592 --> 01:26:06,385
- Mr. Rivetti.
- Sir?

1017
01:26:06,469 --> 01:26:09,013
- Follow me, please.
- Yes, sir.

1018
01:26:24,528 --> 01:26:26,614
Is there a problem, sir?

1019
01:26:30,451 --> 01:26:32,912
These are the keys
to the entire submarine.

1020
01:26:41,420 --> 01:26:46,676
Conn, Weapons. Russian missiles
will have launch capability in 21 minutes.

1021
01:26:47,176 --> 01:26:48,844
Who's in charge here?

1022
01:26:48,886 --> 01:26:50,846
Shit!

1023
01:26:50,888 --> 01:26:53,516
Me, sir. Oh, fuck!

1024
01:26:54,892 --> 01:26:58,521
- How long is it gonna take?
- I don't know, sir.

1025
01:26:58,562 --> 01:27:00,523
- Do you know what's going on?
- Yes.

1026
01:27:00,606 --> 01:27:04,318
No, I don't think you do.
Let me explain it to you.

1027
01:27:04,360 --> 01:27:08,990
If we launch and we're wrong,
what's left of Russia is gonna launch at us.

1028
01:27:09,031 --> 01:27:13,369
There will be a nuclear holocaust beyond
imagination. It's about knowing, Mr...

1029
01:27:13,411 --> 01:27:17,373
Vossler. We have to know whether our
order to launch has been recalled or not.

1030
01:27:17,415 --> 01:27:21,210
The only way we're gonna know is
if you fix that radio. You understand?

1031
01:27:21,294 --> 01:27:23,379
Yes, sir.

1032
01:27:23,504 --> 01:27:26,465
<i>- You ever watch Star Trek?
- Yeah...</i>

1033
01:27:26,549 --> 01:27:29,802
<i>Star Trek. You know, Star Trek,
the USS Enterprise. All right.</i>

1034
01:27:29,885 --> 01:27:33,347
<i>Remember when the Klingons were gonna
blow up the Enterprise? Kirk says:</i>

1035
01:27:33,431 --> 01:27:37,226
- "Scotty, I gotta have more power."
- He needs more warp speed. Yeah.

1036
01:27:37,310 --> 01:27:40,855
Well, I'm Captain Kirk.
You're Scotty. I need more power.

1037
01:27:40,896 --> 01:27:44,442
If you don't get this radio up,
