1038
01:27:44,525 --> 01:27:48,904
I know that's a shitty deal, but you got it.
Can you handle it?

1039
01:27:50,906 --> 01:27:53,034
Scotty?

1040
01:27:55,411 --> 01:27:57,622
Aye, Captain.

1041
01:27:59,624 --> 01:28:01,584
- You got anything?
- No, Vossler.

1042
01:28:01,709 --> 01:28:04,003
Then get on it.

1043
01:28:10,051 --> 01:28:13,137
- I have the conn.
- XO has the conn.

1044
01:28:13,220 --> 01:28:17,433
Chief of the Boat, make your depth
